#compdef biomcp
# ============================================================================
# biomcp - Biomedical Model Context Protocol
#          CLI + MCP server for AI agents
#          (Rust, MIT)
#
# Author : Genomoncology
#           (commercial bioinformatics
#           company; biomcp.org)
# Upstream: https://github.com/genomoncology/biomcp
# Website: https://biomcp.org
#
# `biomcp` is a unified biomedical data
# query CLI + Model Context Protocol (MCP)
# server that exposes structured access to
# major biomedical databases for AI agent
# integration. Provides cross-entity queries
# spanning:
#   - **Genes** (NCBI Gene + Ensembl
#     databases)
#   - **Variants** (ClinVar + dbSNP + COSMIC
#     + VariantValidator)
#   - **Clinical Trials** (clinicaltrials.
#     gov + WHO ICTRP)
#   - **Articles** (PubMed + Europe PMC)
#   - **Drugs** (DrugBank + FDA Orange Book
#     + EMA + DDInter interaction database)
#   - **Diseases** (MONDO + ICD-10 + OMIM)
#   - **Pathways** (Reactome + KEGG)
#   - **Proteins** (UniProt)
#   - **Adverse events** (FDA FAERS)
#   - **PGx (pharmacogenomics)** (PharmGKB)
#
# Architecture:
#   1. **CLI mode**: direct command-line
#      queries (biomcp gene search BRCA1)
#   2. **MCP stdio mode**: AI agent
#      integration via stdin/stdout JSON-RPC
#      (Claude Desktop + Cursor + many AI
#      coding assistants integrate via MCP)
#   3. **MCP HTTP mode**: hosted MCP server
#      for remote agent access (axum-based
#      HTTP server at /mcp endpoint)
#   4. **Local cache management** (HTTP
#     response caching + offline data
#     bundles for EMA + WHO + CDC CVX +
#     DDInter + NCBI GTR)
#
# Distinguishing features:
#   - **MCP-native** (designed primarily
#     for AI agent integration; one of the
#     largest published MCP server
#     implementations in the biomedical
#     domain)
#   - **Genomoncology-backed** (commercial
#     bioinformatics company providing
#     long-term maintenance + clinical-
#     grade data quality)
#   - **Multi-database cross-entity
#     queries** (single query can span
#     genes + variants + trials + articles
#     simultaneously)
#   - **Local data bundles** (FDA + EMA +
#     WHO + CDC data refreshable via
#     offline sync commands; reduces
#     dependence on external API
#     availability)
#   - **Rust performance** (high-throughput
#     query handling for AI agent
#     workloads)
#   - **Both biomcp + biomcp-cli binaries**
#     (biomcp is the unified CLI + server;
#     biomcp-cli is a CLI-only build
#     without server features for slim
#     deployments)
#
# Use cases:
#   - AI clinical decision support agents
#     (Claude/GPT-4 with biomedical
#     knowledge access)
#   - Bioinformatics research workflows
#     (query multiple databases from a
#     single CLI)
#   - Clinical trial discovery for
#     specific conditions or drugs
#   - Variant pathogenicity assessment
#     workflows
#   - Drug interaction screening
#   - Genomics + transcriptomics +
#     proteomics annotation pipelines
#   - AI agent backends for healthcare/
#     biotech companies
#
# Usage:
#   biomcp <command> [args]
#
# Top-level command categories:
#
# Server modes:
#   mcp                            - run MCP
#                                     server
#                                     over
#                                     stdio
#                                     (Claude
#                                     Desktop
#                                     integration)
#   serve                          - alias
#                                     for
#                                     `mcp`
#                                     (Claude
#                                     Desktop
#                                     friendly)
#   serve-http                     - run MCP
#                                     Streamable
#                                     HTTP
#                                     server
#                                     at /mcp
#                                     (canonical
#                                     remote
#                                     deployment;
#                                     axum-
#                                     based)
#
# Entity search + retrieval:
#   search                         - search
#                                     for
#                                     entities
#                                     (sub-
#                                     command:
#                                     all +
#                                     gene +
#                                     drug +
#                                     trial +
#                                     article
#                                     + ...)
#   get                            - get
#                                     entity
#                                     by ID
#                                     (sub-
#                                     command
#                                     by
#                                     entity
#                                     type)
#
# Cross-entity entity helpers:
#   article                        - article
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   variant                        - variant
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#                                     (normalize
#                                     + trials
#                                     + ...)
#   drug                           - drug
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   gene                           - gene
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   disease                        - disease
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   pathway                        - pathway
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   protein                        - protein
#                                     cross-
#                                     entity
#                                     helpers
#   study                          - local
#                                     cBioPortal
#                                     study
#                                     analytics
#
# Local data management:
#   ema                            - EMA
#                                     (European
#                                     Medicines
#                                     Agency)
#                                     local
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   who                            - WHO
#                                     Prequalification
#                                     local
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   who-ivd                        - WHO
#                                     Prequalified
#                                     IVD local
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   cvx                            - CDC
#                                     CVX/MVX
#                                     vaccine
#                                     identity
#                                     local
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   ddinter                        - DDInter
#                                     local
#                                     interaction
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   gtr                            - NCBI
#                                     GTR local
#                                     data
#                                     management
#   cache                          - inspect
#                                     managed
#                                     HTTP
#                                     cache
#
# Discovery + diagnostics:
#   list                           - list
#                                     available
#                                     entities/
#                                     commands
#   discover                       - discover
#                                     entity
#                                     types +
#                                     available
#                                     fields
#   health                         - check
#                                     external
#                                     API
#                                     connectivity
#   chart                          - chart
#                                     type
#                                     documentation
